Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.99,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The famous high school detective Shin'ichi Kudo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:05.66,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}was forced to take a strange poison by a certain organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:08.36,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}causing him to shrink and become Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:09.57,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Doesn't matter if I'm small!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.50,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My mind's that of a brilliant 17-year old detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:14.40,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'll solve another case today that would have adults shaking in their boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:58.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Secret Treasures of the World Exhibit"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:01.06,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:06.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:09.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A map to buried treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.57,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I really liked that gold mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's still tons of secret treasure all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:18.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,that hasn't been discovered yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:21.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?! I wanna try and find some!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:30.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:33.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It has a bunch of strange symbols on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:36.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Maybe it's a treasure map!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:39.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A treasure map?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:45.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you sayin' you can't believe what Ayumi says?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:51.64,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:52.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.64,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:54.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:58.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi's definitely right about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:02.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What if it really is a 100% genuine treasure map?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:05.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! What if it is a real map?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:11.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then! Let's go treasure hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:14.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From this day forth we'll be known as the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:21.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I, Genta Kojima, will be club leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Any objections?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:26.24,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My head's starting to hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a look at that piece of paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this very top symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you seen this somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:05.65,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dino Cavane, the Italian crime lord who was arrested last night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:11.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,at an apartment complex near Tohto Tower, has so far refused to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:16.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The police are currently pursuing Cavane's accomplices,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.06,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but they have been unable to find any clues leading to their whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:21.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The location of the 15,000 Maple Leaf gold coins they stole
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.33,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,is also unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"To Tohto Tower"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:31.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Tohto Tower was suspicious from the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now the treasure is as good as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:38.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you think these letters mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:41.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It says "ORO" here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:43.89,Signs,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,orochi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:43.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,G-Giant serpent?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's an abbreviation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.19,Signs,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,ōkii
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The first O stands for "big"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:51.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The R means rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.63,Signs,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,o-takara
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the last O stands for "treasure"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:59.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that means it's a big treasure that will make you rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I didn't know you could read English, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's a huge treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:16.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm gonna use that treasure to eat the world's best eel dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:18.99,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go around the world 100 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:22.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy a space shuttle from NASA and go into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save it, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how to have fun, do ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:30.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to decipher the code!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But none of the other symbols look like anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:53.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,except for the one that looks like an umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:59.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! It's the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:04.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure must be where the moon and Tohto Tower line up like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's position{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ges everyday,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:13.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and I doubt you could specify exact locations with such simple drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:19.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, did you figure anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:25.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if the other symbols are abbreviations for things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:28.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like this symbol beneath the tower could be a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.33,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath that might be underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:33.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The umbrella beneath that could be an emblem on a sweater or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:37.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the thing that links them all together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A clothes store!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't enough to really—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:43.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Terahara Clothing Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:59.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a clue in here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:11.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid little kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never want to see you here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it didn't have to do with clothing stores after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:19.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I sure am hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go eat something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.65,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:26.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we stop by a bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:29.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! You can't eat anything at a bookstore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a short while. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.99,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, check this out! It's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:44.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"English-to-Japanese Dictionary"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:40.10,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}O. R. O. ORO?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.72,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Was there such a word in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.57,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No luck, it's not in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.56,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.78,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Italian...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.04,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I really doubt it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.85,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:06.79,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oro in Italian means gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:11.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which means this code really does show where treasure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:19.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Mouri Detective Agency"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.16,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The accomplices of the Italian crime lord Dino Cavane,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:19.64,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}who was caught yesterday, are currently in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.27,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The whereabouts of the 15,000 Maple Leaf coins they stole
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.51,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}are, as of yet, unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:29.24,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}These coins, which total over 600 million in Japanese yen, were—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:32.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,600 million, huh? These guys must know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:36.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've trashed the place up again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get any worse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:45.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, where's the runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you mean Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, he left early this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to go to the art museum with his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:53.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kids sure got it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:58.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad! At least help clean up a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.28,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}According to Italian authorities,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:10.12,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}three of Cavane's accomplices are on the run, and one of them is Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:19.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:23.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know? That's all he's been doing since we got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think maybe he figured something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:28.00,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's hopeless! I can't figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.14,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What is this code?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:35.10,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is it a map? Or is it some kind of message?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:43.62,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:47.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See! That sign! It looks just like the second symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:51.06,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could these symbols actually represent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:59.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be! This shop's directly in front of Tohto Tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:03.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and the next symbol has the shape of this sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:08.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So if we follow this order of store signs we'll find the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:11.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But which way should we go from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Moon View Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:24.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could the moon symbol next to the tower actually represent Moon View Street?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it does! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An upside-down triangle sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:37.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It looks just like the third symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:41.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So these symbols really do represent—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:49.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This code is a map from Tohto Tower to the Nanbu Aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:54.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They drew the signs and displays of stores along Moon View Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:57.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the final destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:10:59.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is a mountain of treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:03.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:19.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see the fifth star-shaped symbol anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:23.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! And we were so close to the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've made it all the way to the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.73,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:35.26,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We never even found the fifth symbol on Moon View Street
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:38.37,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}between Tohto Tower and the Nanbu Aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:40.77,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Or am I assuming something incorrectly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:45.24,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait. Why is "gold" written in Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:48.64,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If the person who wrote this was Italian, then the moon symbol...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:00.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We need to go back to where we started!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:17.27,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's hard to think that the person who wrote "gold" in Italian
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:19.71,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}would use the moon symbol to represent Moon View Street—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.81,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}which is in Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:24.14,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The moon represents night—and the things you can only see at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.38,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Neon signs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan! What did you figure out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:34.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a treasure map comprised of the shapes of various neon signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:38.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The neon sign in the second symbol is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:50.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next we go down by the stadium!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to find an umbrella-shaped sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any umbrella-shaped signs anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you've got it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I already found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Tomorrow's Weather"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about? That's the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The symbol for rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rain must've been in the forecast for the day after they wrote the code!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next is a neon sign shaped like a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:24.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A Ferris Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:30.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it! It's the fifth symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So we should see the sixth sign from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:36.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:50.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! The sixth neon sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:00.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Conan, there's really gonna be treasure here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:05.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This symbol has "ORO" written next to it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:09.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for the last fish-shaped sign for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:13.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but I just can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a residential street. There's nothing on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:20.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The closest fish would probably be in a nearby river or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:22.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The river!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:24.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It must mean a river with fish in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:25.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go check out the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:36.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:43.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Quit yer yappin'! The treasure has to be at the bottom of this river!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:51.02,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No! This code represents things you can only see at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:55.52,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So the fish symbol at the end can't represent the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:15:00.13,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If my guess is correct, then it has to be somewhere nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.70,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A fish-shaped neon light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:24.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:25.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The glowing fish, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A glowing fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:37.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:40.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really gonna be a glowing fish here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:46.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's so dark I can't see anything, much less any fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:49.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Towards that river.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The river?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the glowing fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:01.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The lights are reflected on the water and make it look like a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:05.00,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the fish's eye is the light on the building in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean the treasure's in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably located right around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.54,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A gold coin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:31.66,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's that black shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:34.23,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It looks like it's connected to a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.56,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.46,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They raised the sacks of gold coins up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:40.06,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}by looping the rope around part of the ceiling that sticks out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the help, kiddos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:03.32,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Weren't they the ones I saw in front of Tohto Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.29,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait! Maybe they're the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:09.33,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! We found those first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.33,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:11.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\c&H4FAF&\fscx100\fs48}BAM! SMASH! CRASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:22.01,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see. They still don't know where the coins are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Members of that Italian crime ring, most likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Crime ring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:33.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I heard about them on the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means those coins just now must've been—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:43.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We swiped these coins from an Italian bank a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:46.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just like our boss Cavane told us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:50.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But then he backstabbed us and ran off to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:54.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With the 15,000 Maple Leaf coins in tow, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:58.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We tailed him to Japan and paid him a visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But he had hidden the coins somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:07.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't tell us where he hid 'em, no matter how much we interrogated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:11.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All we found at his place was this code!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't help us out, so we informed the police of his location,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:19.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of the coins ourselves, relying only on his code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:24.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The wind blew the paper away when we stopped by the art museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:27.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we saw you cracking the code little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,so we decided to let you keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:34.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never imagined you'd actually find it for us though!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:48.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me! Where are the coins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You better speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:54.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The coins are hidden at the location where the fish symbol
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:02.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and the night view of the bridge outside match up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.64,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:12.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan! What'd you tell him for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:15.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're as good as dead once they find the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:18.86,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They're gonna kill us no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:23.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna shoot us to death, I bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:28.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're gonna stick us in cement and drop us into the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:32.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're going to burn us to death so there's no proof left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.54,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to give up just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we all work together, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:51.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How will that do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're just children!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.62,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we the Detective Boys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get up. But make sure they don't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.27,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We only have one shot at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:21.55,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The moment that they find the coins and let their guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:25.69,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:02.40,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Afterward, we went straight to a nearby police station
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.93,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and explained everything that had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:09.17,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}To everyone's delight, the gang was arrested and the case was closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:12.97,Narration Off,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It wound up being the Detective Boys' very first accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:02.06,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing! All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you cracked that code!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:06.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you even captured some thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was me! I caught them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:11.83,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I used my reasoning to decipher the code!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:15.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't listen to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:22.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} who cracked the code and beat up the gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:26.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:35.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:45.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! You've made a cute little girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:47.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:49.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's embarrassed! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.85,0:23:52.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:23:59.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:06.50,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it! There's still something I want to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.12,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who has the bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:11.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where is it? I can't find—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:21.36,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's only one way to make her believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.36,0:24:24.12,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If I tell her that I'm actually Shin'ichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:27.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.42,0:24:33.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.43,0:24:38.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Cell Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.36,0:24:42.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time's gonna keep you on the edge of your seat. Be sure to watch!
